<UL><UL><UL><UL><UL><UL><UL>
       <LI><FONT size=5>You can see that a word like <FONT color="red"> chronobot</FONT>, which appears 
			in only seven transcripts, is considered twice as significant as a word like 
			<FONT color="green">project</FONT>, which appears in over a hundred.</FONT></LI>
